sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  box Front door
    participant U as User
    participant W as Web
  end
  box Platform
    participant A as API
    participant D as DB
  end

  U->>W: Submit order
  activate W
  par Validate and reserve
    W->>A: Validate payload
    A->>D: Reserve inventory
    D-->>A: Reserved
  and Price quote
    W->>A: Price quote
  end
  A-->>W: Accepted
  W-->>U: Confirmation
  deactivate W

